queries.name: IOT platform - turbine sensors
queries.query: select * from dbdemos_lakehouse_iot.sensor_bronze where turbine_id= '{{ turbine_id }}'

queries.name: IOT platform - turbine status
queries.query: select *, CASE WHEN prediction = 'ok' THEN 'Healthy' ELSE CONCAT('Faulty (', prediction, ')') END as status from dbdemos_lakehouse_iot.current_turbine_metrics where turbine_id= '{{ turbine_id }}'
